  "instructions": [
    "Combine fish, garlic, mixture powder, lemon juice, butter, onion, carrots, and potatoes in a large steamer basket.",
    "Place the steamer basket over boiling water, making sure the fish is not touching the water.",
    "Cover the pot with a lid and steam for 10 minutes.",
    "Remove the fish and vegetables from the steamer and divide them among four plates.",
    "Serve immediately, garnished with fresh parsley if desired."
